  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time portfolio tracking for STX and sBTC balances",
    "AI-powered DeFi strategy recommendations with personalized risk profiling",
    "Yield calculator for simulating returns across Stacks DeFi protocols",
    "Stacking position management and reward tracking",
    "Portfolio health score based on diversification and risk analysis",
    "Protocol comparison tool with APY, TVL, and risk metrics",
    "On-chain user profile and strategy history via Clarity smart contracts",
    "Non-custodial wallet integration with Leather and Xverse"
